      "content": "---\ntitle: 德国税收简述\nupdated: 2019-03-30 19:41:53Z\ncreated: 2019-03-30 19:23:38Z\nauthor: tangyongfeng@gmail.com\n---\n\n\n<en-note><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">众所周知,德国税务体系复杂，其中工资税是非常重要的一个税种，工资税的多少，直接影响着一个家庭或者个人的收入水平和生活质量。您是否明白德国工资税的等级划分，是否清楚哪种税级最适合您。欧通商务咨询会为您这篇文章中详细介绍有关a德国工资税的知识。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">什么是德国工资税等级?</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">德国工资税等级（简称&ldquo;税级&rdquo;，德语叫做Steuerklasse）是每个人缴纳个人工资收入所得税的重要依据，每个人的税卡上都会有税级体现。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">德国工资税等级有哪些?分别适用于哪些人士?</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">德国工资税的税级共分一到六级。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">一级税级（Steuerklasse I）的适合人士是：</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 单身未婚人士。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 离异人士。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 丧偶人士，凡其伴侣在2014年1月1日之前去世。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 已婚人士，其配偶一方生活在国外或者双方长期分居的情况。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">二级税级（Steuerklasse II）的适合人士是：</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 符合一定条件的单亲家庭的父亲或母亲。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">所需符合的条件有：孩子户口必须登记在父亲或母亲的住址处，如果孩子在父母双方处报户口的话， 则由领取儿童金的一方获得二级税级。单亲的父亲或母亲没有登记的同居伴侣。单亲家庭只有父亲或母亲与至少一个未成年孩子，不可以有其他的成年人同住。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">三级税级（Steuerklasse III）的适合人士是：</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 已婚人士，夫妻双方共同居住在德国境内，没有长期分居，并且夫妻另一方拿五级税级。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 丧偶人士，其伴侣于2014年1月1日之后去世。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">四级税级（Steuerklasse IV）的适合人士是：</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 已婚人士，夫妻双方共同居住在德国境内，没有长期分居，并且夫妻另一方拿四级税级。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 登记的同居人士。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">五级税级（Steuerklasse V）的适合人士是：</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 已婚人群，夫妻双方共同居住在德国境内，没有长期分居，并且夫妻另一方拿三级税级。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">六级税级（Steuerklasse VI）的适合人士是：</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 同时兼任几份工作的人士。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">不同的税级对需缴纳工资税到底有多大影响？</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">一个年薪为40000欧元的人士，如果他持一级税卡，他需缴纳的年工资税额为6521欧元。如果他持二级税卡，他需缴纳的年工资税额为6127欧元。如果他持三级税卡，他需缴纳的年工资税额为3434欧元。如果他持四级税卡，他需缴纳的年工资税额为6521欧元。如果他持五级税卡，他需缴纳的年工资税额为10658欧元。如果他持六级税卡，他需缴纳的年工资税额为11093欧元。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">从中可见一级税卡和四级税卡的需缴纳税额是一样的。三级税卡需缴纳税额最少，六级税卡需缴纳税额最多。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">不过以上列出的工资税额都是预缴税额,具体的年工资税额是在报税以后税务局针对每个纳税人的情况计算出结果。预缴过多的话就会收到退税，预缴过少的话就要补税。尽管最后缴税额是一样的，但是纳税人还是应该根据自己的具体情况选择对自己最有利的税级，让自己现在就能缴最少的税，拿到最多的净工资。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">对于已婚人士来说，税级组合有几种可能性？分别适用于哪些情况？</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">已婚人士的税级组合有以下三种可能性:</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">三五级组合: 如果一方配偶比另一方的工资高很多，用三五级组合对整个家庭比较有利。在这种组合下，工资高的一方持三级税卡，付的工资税要少很多。工资低的一方持五级税卡，需缴相对较高的工资税。选择三五级组合的夫妻有报税义务，第二年报税时，税务局根据双方工资总额计算决定，是否有多缴的工资税退回还是需补缴不足的工资税。如果持三级税卡的一方工资非常高，并且没有很多的抵税开销的话，那么这种组合很可能会导致需补缴税款。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">四四级组合: 如果夫妻双方的工资差不多，那么可以选择四四级组合，即双方都持四级税卡。选择四四级组合的夫妻没有报税义务，但是如果有可以抵税的开销的话，通过报税一般都可以退回一些多缴的税款。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">带参数的四四级组合: 这个新的组合是上述三五级组合和四四级组合的综合体。如果夫妻一方因收入较低而持五级税卡的话，纯收入是比持四级税卡要低的，为了解决这个有点不公平的问题，税务局从2010年开始引入了这个新的组合，在计算预缴税时，税务局会综合考虑该夫妻全年的应交税总额，然后除以四四级组合的缴税总额，得出一个参数，在四四级的基础上乘上这个参数就是夫妻每月需缴纳的税额。用这样的算法夫妻双方的纯收入的分配就比三五组合要公平一些了。选择这个组合的夫妻没有报税义务，并且即使报税，也基本不会有很大的退税金额或补交金额的情况出现。</span></div><p STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"></p><div><br/></div><div STYLE=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"font-size: 12pt;-en-paragraph:true;\">什么情况下需要变更税级？</span></div><p></p><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">如果您的家庭状况和职业状况发生改变，就需要申请变更税级，比如:</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 结婚。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 分居或离婚。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 丧偶。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 变成单亲家庭。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\"> 开始第二，第三职业等等。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">如何变更税级？</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">一般情况下，您每年有一次变更税级的机会，如果因夫妻中的一人失业或离世等情况而需要变更税级的，则不受次数限制。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">您需要完整填写&ldquo;变更税级申请表&ldquo;(Antrag auf Steuerklassenwechsel bei Ehegatten)并签字，面交或邮寄给您居住地管辖区的税务局。申请表您可以直接在税务局的网站上下载，或者在以下链接</span><a HREF=\"http://steuerklassen.biz/Steuerklassenwechsel.pdf\" STYLE=\"color: rgb(36, 145, 202); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; outline: none;-en-paragraph:true;\">http://steuerklassen.biz/Steuerklassenwechsel.pdf</a><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">下载。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">如何把四四级组合改为带参数的四四级组合？</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">如果您想把现有的四四级组合变成带参数的四四级组合，则也需通过更改税级的流程。您和配偶需共同填写&ldquo;变更税级申请表&ldquo;(Antrag auf Steuerklassenwechsel bei Ehegatten)和，以及给出当年的工资金额的预测值，并签字后面交或邮寄给您居住地管辖区的税务局。申请表您可以直接在税务局的网站上下载，或者在以下链接</span><a HREF=\"http://steuerklassen.biz/Steuerklassenwechsel.pdf\" STYLE=\"color: rgb(36, 145, 202); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; outline: none;-en-paragraph:true;\">http://steuerklassen.biz/Steuerklassenwechsel.pdf</a><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;-en-paragraph:true;\">下载。</span></div></en-note>      ",
